## Step 4 — Record results

Update two files:

**`.sdlc/premortem.md`** — append this pre-mortem session with date, feature, risks, and mitigations.

**`.sdlc/risk-register.md`** — add new risks with their scores. The risk register is the living log reviewed at each planning session.
